title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 6 categories of Region on the x axis representing 2 groups: Males, and Females.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Region East Asia with a mean value of 77.5.
The lowest category is observed at South Asia that has a mean value of 69.5
showing a difference of 10.9% with the maximum value.
In case of East Asia, Males shows more dominance than any other Region with a value 75.0 and it has the lowest value 68.0 in South Asia.
